org.fhnw.aigs.commons.communication

Class GameStartMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fhnw.aigs.commons.communication.Message
      • org.fhnw.aigs.commons.communication.GameStartMessage

  • public class GameStartMessage
extends Message
    This message is sent by the server as soon as the player was identified, a join message has been sent and a game has enough participants for a new game. It will inform all clients of a game about the game.
    Additionally the "startingPlayer" indicates who is going to start the game.
